好多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就假設當初2003年成功立法 <br />\n但到2019年又係發生大型示威<br />\n我估到時建制又會動員輿論 話23條唔夠辣 要加辣先夠 <br />\n所以 無論如何 只要管治手法不變<br />\n香港個終局都係一樣 只係個過程+IMPACT唔同"},{"pid":"c47ffdcbb8db1fbcbedfec8cec77f221d278d1fa","tid":2224034,"uid":19165,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:22:00.000Z","msg":"支共小學雞諗野方式真係好奇特, 一般人如果見到政策反對聲音大就一定覺得係政策有問題所以收回, 係支共小學雞邏輯底下就會掉轉, 佢先有前設用鬥爭論覺得有一班人係不可被教化, 必須消滅, 所以後來諗既所有政策都係以&quot;如何有效地消滅一小撮人&quot;為原則, 當佢見到香港人反應好大, 佢就同噴殺蟲水d 蟲會跑走一樣覺得&quot;無錯係有效既！&quot;. <br />\n<br />\n所以無謂呃自己, 從此邏輯往上推, 支共唯一目的就係要消滅反抗既香港人, join them or perish"},{"pid":"8dec11c021f964e36577559355a4229b47c94e0b","tid":2224034,"uid":209097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:22:40.000Z","msg":"係隻開槍狗on9 明明唔開嗰槍應該無咁大noise<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0d51c91621f3a33d8681aad55812976338b0bf","tid":2224034,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"371f324f220f1cb3df97bc57b05f4c388201f485","tid":2224034,"uid":48083,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:08:51.000Z","msg":"關乜事<br />\n澳門夠哂聽話啦<br />\n咪又係乜法都立齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:25:34.000Z","msg":"所以呢啲真係聽下就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b47e8be28a4d307c2ec8c547966e0f5229db7d29","tid":2224034,"uid":336524,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"04a539dbe98b0415b4d8ca082a1d6c0ab04c7bd4","tid":2224034,"uid":231480,"like":127,"dislike":45,"score":82,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kceUKL5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-s